Html:
I would love to hear your feedback! 

Please use the issue tracker if you find any bugs, and I'll try to fix them ASAP.

 

As you might have noticed, RateIt supports custom stars, and also range images (see the signal/antenna example). It would also be great if you could share your custom artwork you use for your RateIt plugin, so we can create some repository here to share with the rest of the people.
